module emoji

context-free start-symbols Start

context-free syntax

    Start = {Exp "\n"}+

    Exp.Add = Exp PLUS Exp
    Exp.Var = ID

lexical syntax

    PLUS = [\0x2795]
    ID = [\0x1f600-\0x1f645]+ // From "grinning" to "rolling eyes". https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emoji#Unicode_blocks
    LAYOUT = [\ \t\r]
